ues that both Derrida and Paul are indispensable guides to a new way of thinking about justice.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aRELIGION / Biblical Criticism & Interpretation / New Testament.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362557040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503625570423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503625570/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles